@Node "elektrik.empire" "[                                              what is elektrik empire."
@Next "ele.releases"
@Prev "Main"
@Toc "Main"

                             @{b}ele@{ub} - @{fg shine}elektrik empire@{fg text}

   elektrik empire is a artic musiek group (norwegian, finnish and swedish).

   the group was founded late 1997 by acidpimp (also known as snap/avt) and
   caustic, but back then we called us  `the asvalt project` . Now sami has
   joined us from finland. 


@EndNode

@Node "ele.releases" "[                                                 ele releases in 1997."
@Next "ele.members"
@Prev "ele.releases"
@Toc "Main"

                             @{b}ele@{ub} - @{fg shine}information@{fg text}

   the releases will be found on thease following sites, we use a "ele_"*.lha
   so they should not be that hard to find, or what?

   guest releases are also welcome, so _please_ contact us if you want to
   release sumething under the elektrik empire label.

   @{b}ftp@{ub} - ftp.uni-paderborn.de - pub/aminet/mods/misc/ele_<rel>.lha
   lha-versions.
   @{b}www@{ub} - http://pzykotik.ml.org/elektrik/releases.html (offical homepage)
       http://www.geocities.com/sunsetstrip/pallodium/5078/releases.html
   lha-versions.

   @{b}bbs@{ub} - norwegian hq            - raw power ..... +47-577-43-602 - cwetdrug
         swedish hq              - wanted    ..... +xx-xxx-xx-xxx - wanted
         finnish hq              - wanted    ..... +xx-xxx-xx-xxx - wanted

                             @{b}ele@{ub} - @{fg shine}releases 1997@{fg text}

   [            01.tragix.caustic.protracker.19-feb-97.125bpm, 341kb, 08.33min.
   [                                               pumpin' acid."avt_trax.lha".

   [      02.im my brain.acidpimp.protracker.18-sep-97.125bpm, 288kb, 07.03min.
   [                                         vierdelectrosounds."ele_mind.lha".

   [             03.the end.caustic.octamed.07-may-97.125bpm, 1223kb, 09.13min.
   [   special multipart caustic style,futuring marianne grytten."ele_end.lha".

   [      04a.humaan lintuni - side a.sami.xm.27-10-97.xxxbpm, 178kb, 03.91min.
   [              side a of the velocity ep by sami, acid house."ele_velo.lha".

   [          04b.transition - side b.sami.xm.27-10-97.xxxbpm, 373kb, 04.12min.
   [    side b of the velocity ep by sami, tripping acid trance."ele_velo.lha".

